About Us
Specialising in design and fabrication of FIA, CAMS and ANDRA approved roll over protection systems for any vehicle. With over 35 years experience in specialised motorsport fabrication in Perth, Western Australia, you can be assured that your custom project will be completed to the highest possible TIG welding standard.
While Roll Cages are our specialty, call to enquire about custom fabrication of other products.
